<TITLE> Tax-free income limit rises for women </TITLE>
<TEXT>
 Dhaka, June 9 (bdnews24.com)  The finance adviser Monday proposed to raise the tax-free income ceiling by Tk 15,000 to Tk 165,000 for women tax-payers and those aged over 70. AB Mirza Azizul Islam in his televised budget speech said the existing limit for tax-free income of Tk 150,000 would remain uncharged for others in fiscal 2008-09. "It may be mentioned that the limit for tax free income was considerably raised in the last fiscal year," he said. bd
